Consumables.title: Adrenaline Syringe
Consumables.desc: Adrenaline Syringes increase a character's boost by 100 instantly. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it.

Consumables.title: Energy Drink
Consumables.desc: Energy Drinks increase a character's boost by 40 instantly. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it.

Consumables.title: Painkiller
Consumables.desc: Painkillers increase a character's boost by 60 instantly. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it.

Consumables.title: Bandage
Consumables.desc: Bandages heal a character's health by 10 overtime. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it. It cannot heal character's health over 75.

Consumables.title: First Aid Kit
Consumables.desc: First Aid Kits heal a character's health to 75 instantly. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it. This item cannot be used when player's health is over 75.

Consumables.title: Med Kit
Consumables.desc: Med Kits heal a character's health to 100 instantly. Performing certain actions while casting this item will cancel it.

Consumables.title: Gas Can
Consumables.desc: You can refuel vehicles with it.
